<br>
The only time the T-Staff outstrips the Amy is when I get a solid 3-4 procs per fight, with around a 5 second stun per stun.  Until you have both in your Tink, and can compare them side-by-side I really don't think your qualified to expouse expert opinion....just my 2 cents.<br>
